DP Ruto has also taken the war on President Kenyatta’s allies to their doorsteps, including Mr Koinange, the chairman. Over the weekend, he toured Mr Koinange’s Kiambaa Constituency in Kiambu, where speakers took on the MP who supports President Kenyatta’s Kieleweke faction of Jubilee. 

Speaking to a vernacular station Monday, Mr Koinange said that he will not be intimidated by the visits and attempts to impose candidates in the constituency. 



